wiki.content: 'Te Amo' ('I Love You' in spanish) is the 3rd international (5th overall) single of Rated R and according to 'Te Amo Songfacts', the Stargate produced song, in which a wise woman warns the narrator "Don't let love hurt you," is Rihanna's paean to her international audience.
